<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
	<head>
		<meta charset="UTF-8" />
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
		<title>EMA624_04_IH_0002</title>

		<!-- 공통 js-->
		<script src="../../common_contents/common/js/app.js"></script>
		<script src="../../common_practice/common/js/solve_area_act.js"></script>

		<!-- 공통 css-->
		<link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/common/css/app.css" />

		<!-- 개별 -->
		<link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_practice/common/css/app.css" />
		<link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_practice/css/ema624_04.css" />
	</head>

	<body>
		<div id="app_wrap" class="ema624_04_ih_0002">
			<section class="title type2">
				<h2 data-head="2_deep_green">
					<span lang="y">비의 성질을 이용하여 비례식을 세우려고 합니다.</span>
					<span class="empty_box nemo"></span>
					<span lang="y">안에 알맞은 수를 써넣으세요.</span>
				</h2>
			</section>

			<section class="contents">
				<div class="question_box justify_center dir_col">
					<div class="box_area box1">
						<img src="./../../common_practice/img/EMA624_04_IH/0002_01_bg.png" alt="" />
						<div class="text_area">
							<div class="l_left">
								<img src="./../../common_practice/img/EMA624_04_IH/0002_lines.png" alt="" />
								<p class="text1">6:11</p>
								<div class="text2">
									18:
									<div class="input_wrap">
										<math-field data-answer-single="33"></math-field>
									</div>
								</div>
								<div class="input_position input1">
									×
									<div class="input_wrap">
										<math-field data-answer-single="3"></math-field>
									</div>
								</div>
								<div class="input_position input2">
									×
									<div class="input_wrap"><math-field data-answer-single="3"></math-field></div>
								</div>
							</div>
							<div class="l_right">
								<div class="text_row">
									<span lang="y">6:11은 전항과 후항에</span>
									<div class="input_wrap">
										<math-field data-answer-single="3"></math-field>
									</div>
									<span lang="y">을/를 곱한</span>
								</div>
								<div class="text_row">
									<span>18:</span>
									<div class="input_wrap">
										<math-field data-answer-single="33"></math-field>
									</div>
									<span lang="y">과/와 그 비율이 같습니다.</span>
								</div>
								<div class="text_row">
									<p lang="y">두 비를 이용하여 비례식을 세우면</p>
								</div>
								<div class="text_row">
									<span>6:11=18:</span>
									<div class="input_wrap">
										<math-field data-answer-single="33"></math-field>
									</div>
									<span lang="y">입니다.</span>
								</div>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="box_area box2 mt_20">
						<img src="./../../common_practice/img/EMA624_04_IH/0002_02_bg.png" alt="" />
						<div class="text_area">
							<div class="l_left">
								<img src="./../../common_practice/img/EMA624_04_IH/0002_lines_02.png" alt="" />
								<p class="text1">30:45</p>
								<div class="text2">
									<div class="input_wrap">
										<math-field data-answer-single="2"></math-field>
									</div>
									:3
								</div>
								<div class="input_position input1">
									÷
									<div class="input_wrap">
										<math-field data-answer-single="15"></math-field>
									</div>
								</div>
								<div class="input_position input2">
									÷
									<div class="input_wrap"><math-field data-answer-single="15"></math-field></div>
								</div>
							</div>
							<div class="l_right">
								<div class="text_row">
									<span lang="y">30:45는 전항과 후항을</span>
									<div class="input_wrap">
										<math-field data-answer-single="15"></math-field>
									</div>
									<span lang="y">(으)로 나눈</span>
								</div>
								<div class="text_row">
									<div class="input_wrap">
										<math-field data-answer-single="2"></math-field>
									</div>
									<span lang="y">:3과 그 비율이 같습니다.</span>
								</div>
								<div class="text_row">
									<p lang="y">두 비를 이용하여 비례식을 세우면</p>
								</div>
								<div class="text_row">
									<span>30:45=</span>
									<div class="input_wrap">
										<math-field data-answer-single="2"></math-field>
									</div>
									<span lang="y">:3입니다.</span>
								</div>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
				<!-- 해설 -->
				<div class="solve_area">
					<div class="inner_solve">
						<div class="flex">
							<strong class="tit_solve" lang="y">해설</strong>
							<div class="conts_solve">
								<p>
									6 : 11은 전항과 후항에 3을 곱한 18 : 33과 그 비율이 같습니다. 두 비를 이용하여
									<br />비례식을 세우면 6 : 11=18 : 33입니다.
								</p>
								<p>
									30 : 45는 전항과 후항을 15로 나눈 2 : 3과 그 비율이 같습니다. 두 비를 이용하여
									<br />비례식을 세우면 30 : 45=2 : 3입니다.
								</p>
							</div>
						</div>
						<div class="buttons_solve"></div>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="btn_area">
					<button class="btnType key">입력타입토글</button>
					<button class="btnReset">리셋</button>
					<button class="btnCheck">확인</button>
				</div>
			</section>
		</div>
	</body>
</html>
